    "value_statement": "Teams often need one interface for many hosted AI models and media tools. This skill guides Claude, Codex, and Claude Code through inference.sh CLI commands for discovery, execution, and task review.",
    "seo_keywords": [
      "Claude inference.sh skill",
      "Codex AI CLI",
      "Claude Code agent tools",
      "inference.sh CLI",
